kw.name: Open Chrome for Linux And Navigate To SS
kw.doc: Sets up the Chrome envrionment for the Linux, displayless image. This will run in the Jenkins job on the Docker container's Ubuntu image. This means that there's no real display for the browser to run in and, thereofre, it requires a virtual display to run correctly. It uses the Xvfb library.

kw.name: Too Many Requests Check
kw.doc: This is a check for the 'Too Many Requests' instance. When you try to login to Site Scan more than 5 times (?) within 30 seconds (?) you will get an error message reading 'Too many requests. Retry in 60 seconds.'. If that happens, the login keyword will fail (it's expecting to see the map after clicking Login). This check catches that issue.
